channel.title: My server has been up, but now people can't get on
channel.description:
Anyone have any Ideas to why no one can get on my server? Of course I can still get on it without typing an IP and connecting. But no one is able to connect with my IP...
I went to sleep and it was running, I woke up and my computer was restarted and when i turned my server on, no one that plays it normally could log on. If there are any pictures someone needs to see, or if i posted this in the wrong area, please let me know.
